{"tid":822123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"風暴山竹造成嚴重破壞 教協建議教育局宣佈明天停課","createTime":"2018-09-16T07:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T09:07:46.000Z","uid":111093,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b44fc93cd3691cd1295bc4199581b94d4efa0942","tid":822123,"uid":111093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"（新聞稿，2018年9月16日，13:50）颱風山竹吹襲本港，在各區造成嚴重破壞，多區均有樹木倒塌及建築物受破壞。由於預計本港今日繼續受到颶風影響，道路交通在風暴後需時回復正常，加上校方亦需時檢查校舍受破壞的情況。基於保障學生安全，教協於今日中午聯絡教育局，建議當局盡早宣佈明天所有學校停課，讓學校在明天先檢查校舍情況，才於星期二正式復課。教協期望教育局盡早作出決定，讓校方有足夠時間安排相關人手及校舍檢查工作。"},{"pid":"0dc5d22286a976d80fd9aa55911fe4660000f05c","tid":822123,"uid":125213,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:37:07.000Z","msg":"強烈反對停課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我聽日dayoff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd1573fe9467eed3ccc6b48956f557c6f6b50f4","tid":822123,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:41:16.000Z","msg":"少少事停咩課呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa3ccbdcbf45941773c46a5aae0fb55543ab9e4d","tid":822123,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"冇得返學<br />\n好唔開心"},{"pid":"a74457f6ec9d631d26ccc2de27fc6f920e2279b9","tid":822123,"uid":9286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T09:07:46.000Z","msg":"返唔到學但返到工<br />\n神奇邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}